vin Gluskie</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/hakan-gurdal">Hakan Gurdal</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/ernest-jelito">Ernest Jelito</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/jon-morrish">Jon Morrish</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="/en/chris-ward">Chris Ward</a></li></ul></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/supervisory-board">Supervisory Board</a></li><li class="expanded"><a href="/en/corporate-governance" title="">Corporate Governance</a><ul class="menu level-2"><li class="first leaf"><a href="/en/declaration-of-corporate-governance" title="">Declaration of Corporate Governance</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/articles-of-association" title="">Articles of Association</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/remuneration-report">Remuneration Report</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/managers-transactions">Managers&#039; Transactions</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="/en/rules-of-procedure-for-the-supervisory-board">Rules of Procedure for the Supervisory Board</a></li></ul></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/en/purchasing" title="">Supplier and Purchasing Information</a><div class="megalayer-content"><div class="medium-6 columns"><div class="box lighter"><div class="entity entity-megalayer megalayer-element clearfix">
